{"tid":1189473,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本JK：「癡漢請住手」 搭電車上學的女高中生等90人聚集表訴求","createTime":"2019-06-06T21:00:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-06T23:46:48.000Z","uid":5338,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a4cc69bb16871439392e2c9df2e868373b9c30ba","tid":1189473,"uid":5338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T21:00:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://public.potaufeu.asahi.com/5e76-p/picture/16549576/35b94cfd2c9f866b36b30c0611e205bd_640px.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpublic.potaufeu.asahi.com%2F5e76-p%2Fpicture%2F16549576%2F35b94cfd2c9f866b36b30c0611e205bd_640px.jpg&h=921b8cc5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://public.potaufeu.asahi.com/7a14-p/picture/16549577/a8188be589a204acb42225ee70ab18cb_640px.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpublic.potaufeu.asahi.com%2F7a14-p%2Fpicture%2F16549577%2Fa8188be589a204acb42225ee70ab18cb_640px.jpg&h=e477c20a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n「癡漢（色狼）請住手」。位於JR川越線與東武東上線的川越站，5日早上約有90名搭電車上學、就讀當地山村學園高中的女學生等人，在現場透過發放面紙等方式向通勤上班、上學的乘客表達訴求。<br />\n<br />\n  此為埼玉縣警鐵路警察隊的宣導活動，該高中收到來自鐵警隊的委託，協助招募參加活動的學生，然而最後聚集的人數多到連鐵警隊長也驚訝地說是「意料之外」。<br />\n<br />\n  在每年6月女性衣著變薄之際，鐵警隊均會展開防治癡漢行為的宣導活動。身穿制服的學生們戴上寫有「癡漢是犯罪」的黃色活動肩帶，並發放附有傳單的紙製口罩，單子上條列了「如果遇到癡漢行為」、「為了抓住犯人」等各項應對方法。當天也出現大聲喊著「拜託了」，熱心投入宣導的男學生身影。<br />\n<br />\n  現年17歲、搭乘西武新宿線上學的高3女學生表示：「也有過在電車內被緊盯著看的恐怖經驗，朋友中也有人被摸過屁股。如果看到有人受害，希望大家不要視若無睹，能出聲說『住手』、『沒事吧』之類的來幫忙。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://asahichinese-f.com/society/12433619\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fasahichinese-f.com%2Fsociety%2F12433619&d=KA2pTlu%2BoVpRwWZcRxs8e4bCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=66a4c4fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://asahichinese-f.com/society/12433619</a>"},{"pid":"e98443b2cc75a0cc247713d3d244e4efe26496e2","tid":1189473,"uid":238309,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T21:44:07.000Z","msg":"最緊要係千奇唔好啞忍"},{"pid":"f696b9e2f31161a194f8da9d14538b658cae9174","tid":1189473,"uid":24339,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T21:46:52.000Z","msg":"幼幼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"860c600181c62546d32c9cc5bce6b371a7307da9","tid":1189473,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T21:51:15.000Z","msg":"相：我們中出了一個男生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8eba310b81db0ddd5f2ccdf6283ac664ff1413b1","tid":1189473,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T22:54:26.000Z","msg":"仲會多咗囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7263f8b3a4a35f72ea4429d25f3a9ba235f3760b","tid":1189473,"uid":5338,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T22:58:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8964855eb6de975570a2701a540aeb5d56006506","tid":1189473,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T23:00:03.000Z","msg":"後面班男仔做乜9, 唔通男都比人落手 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9864d4cefc351671e53bba2925f412b16e2f29ec","tid":1189473,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T23:02:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cb4aa706abb42c301348063885940b32963df005","tid":1189473,"uid":90704,"like":2,"dislike":11,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T23:15:50.000Z","msg":"了下個西都話非禮<br />\n唔好出街啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2539ed0b8d8f8a865cb3627a075b802082145ae9","tid":1189473,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T23:46:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}